26
00:01:23.820 --> 00:01:26.040
This is modern understanding

27
00:01:27.520 --> 00:01:31.430
about mitochondrial cancer metabolism.

28
00:01:33.840 --> 00:01:37.680
Of course, mitochondria produce ATP through OXPHOS

29
00:01:37.780 --> 00:01:40.620
