For example,

35
00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:56.760
biogenesis and turnover

36
00:01:58.680 --> 00:01:59.420
dynamics,

37
00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:01.760
evasion of cell death,

38
00:02:02.840 --> 00:02:04.580
oxidative stress control,

39
00:02:05.480 --> 00:02:09.330
of course, signal transduction, and metabolic reprogramming.

40
00:02:10.741 --> 00:02:11.240
So,

41
00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:15.640
to understand such mitochondria, we have to

42
