And third speaker, Luca,

90
00:04:55.340 --> 00:04:59.160
will show potential for therapeutic application

91
00:04:59.240 --> 00:05:03.040
using mitochondria transfer. So we are moving

92
00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:07.620
traditional Warburg effect into

