00:17:25.108 --> 00:17:27.268
the non-denervated versus

302
00:17:28.449 --> 00:17:32.068
denervated tumor to check at the change at the transcriptional level.

303
00:17:32.668 --> 00:17:35.748
And long story short, what we found was striking.

