359
00:20:41.660 --> 00:20:45.600
So this was documenting the transfer at the nerve cancer interface, and we

360
00:20:45.640 --> 00:20:49.420
wanted to see, before moving forward, if it was a true reality

361
00:20:49.680 --> 00:20:53.400
in human samples. So we took these samples, and that's a

362
00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:55.280
collaboration with Dr. Gustavo Ayala.

363
00:20:56.040 --> 00:20:59.920
We took these samples about perineural invasion occurring, which is very frequent

