00:21:04.020 --> 00:21:07.240
brown and around are the cancer cells that are wrapping around the nerves.

366
00:21:07.700 --> 00:21:11.600
And what we did label is the mitochondria into these cancer cells, and by

367
00:21:11.660 --> 00:21:15.440
using AI-based segmentation as well as multispectral

368
00:21:15.520 --> 00:21:19.380
imaging, we quantify the quantity of mitochondria per cell on

369
00:21:19.440 --> 00:21:23.340
the patient samples. And what we found is

370
00:21:24.860 --> 00:21:28.780
the closest the cancer cells are to the nerves, the highest is

